(71, 1, '2017-09-26 07:36:41', '2017-09-26 07:36:41', 'Email Template\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<table style=\"border: 1px solid #ccc; margin-top: 10px;\" border=\"0\" width=\"600\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" align=\"center\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<table border=\"0\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"20\" align=\"center\"><!-- -->\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr align=\"center\">\r\n<td style=\"font-family: arial; padding-bottom: 40px;\"><strong>\r\n<img src=\"[LOGO]\" alt=\"logo\" /></strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<!-- --></tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<table style=\"border: 0px solid #efefef; margin-top: 0px; padding: 40px;\" border=\"0\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"10\" align=\"center\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<h2>Hi [NAME],</h2>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<h4>This is an automated email from us at Time About as it looks like [PARENT2] has now declined your requested arrangement three times.</h4>\r\nIf you believe you are receiving this message in error or the arrangement you originally requested is redundant you can send us an email by reply to this message and we will reset your requested arrangement. This will then allow you to start over. Please allow up to 24 hours for the reset to take effect (we will notify you).\r\n\r\nIf however the requested arrangement is just not going to be accepted and you are at an impasse with [PARENT2] then don\'t despair, we are still here to help. Just hit REPLY to this email and in the SUBJECT line type \"DISPUTE RESOLUTION\" and we will then send you out some details about how to resolve your issues and get your parenting arrangements on track as soon as possible.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<table border=\"0\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<h3>Regards</h3>\r\n<h3>The Team @ Time About</h3>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"30\"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<table style=\"border: 0px solid #efef